{"tid":392402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨稱必定追究奚落標語事件犯人","createTime":"2017-09-08T13:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T17:02:12.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7be3820f4c84a66269ee3b480296b82799815d29","tid":392402,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"教大民主牆張貼冒犯蔡若蓮字句　馬時亨稱追究到底<br />\n<br />\n教育局副局長蔡若蓮長子墮樓身亡後，有人於教育大學民主牆張貼冒犯字句，教大學生會其後移除有關大字報。<br />\n<br />\n教育大學校董會主席馬時亨表示，校方正調查張貼大字報的人是否教大的學生，校方會追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n被問到如果證實是學生所為，會否開除學生，馬時亨說，要按校方的既定程序處理，他希望香港人反省事件，反問家長是否希望張貼大字報的人，日後成為自己子女的老師。<br />\n<br />\n對於有傳媒公布疑似張貼大字報人士的容貌，馬時亨說，校方沒有發表過相關相片，亦不知相片是如何流出，重申校方會追查事件。"},{"pid":"8f9ffed87c6d25aa3097192fe3d6a020ac25a7f7","tid":392402,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"犯法咪?"},{"pid":"ac26bd76c849f2140eab56e6deefcf99ae77d729","tid":392402,"uid":53278,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:04:25.000Z","msg":"唔撚俾恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n惡撚過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26813c1ad612b309ef8136b89f4ded7ae0c9028","tid":392402,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"犯乜撚野人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c4d0b2ef4f88b8a5bc6c4298959e58e6738081","tid":392402,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>犯法咪?</blockquote><br />\n好快釋法"},{"pid":"29966cb0334f20424392fb5dcb8a1ac343effdd4","tid":392402,"uid":82640,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n犯校規<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你禁止佢坐地鐵囉<br />\n私人公司大撚哂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cl